short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Make it easier to print the full section of a service manual for your Subaru from STIS Website

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Subaru Technical Information System (STIS) has HTML-based versions of Service Manuals for Subaru Vehicles.

These HTML service manuals allow you to print a chapter or subsection of the service manual but not the full section.

This extension will add a "Section" button to the "Print" submenu and generate the printable full section.
